exif:ImageDescription: King, Tripp opened up about her decision to get plastic surgery, which she said was fueled by scrutiny from the press during the Clinton scandal and by comedian John Goodman's unflattering impression of her on Saturday Night Live..."I was so shattered for my children," she said. "Kids are so sensitive about their parents anyway. And my kids always thought I was pretty. And they were so completely shattered...I just felt so badly for them. I just wanted to fix it."
